        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n@Jessica Can you please help me with the issue I am facing in Jenkins Sandbox:\n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/sandbox/view/All/job/ccsdk-oran-maven-clm-master/1/console\n\nAs you can see, the maven build succeeds but then the job fails:\n\n20:47:22 [ccsdk-oran-maven-clm-master] $ /bin/bash /tmp/jenkins244428125753935044.sh\n20:47:22 [ccsdk-oran-maven-clm-master] $ /bin/sh -xe /tmp/jenkins2260632076908144039.sh\n20:47:22 + find . -regex .*karaf/target\n20:47:22 + xargs rm -rf\n20:47:24 ERROR: Build step failed with exception\n20:47:24 java.lang.IllegalArgumentException: The application ID onap-ccsdk-oran is invalid.\n\nDo I need to configure onap-ccsdk-oran somewhere? I am new to the CLM stuff, so please help me how can I proceed.\n\nThanks!",
